[00:20.05] O, lover! O, desire!
[00:30.05] 
[00:58.44] In the heavy heat of endless night
[01:02.85] the sun will rise again and bring new light
[01:07.67] I am whole beneath the midnight moon
[01:12.07] the sun comes far too soon
[01:25.07] 
[01:35.04] When I found you in the deepest darkness
[01:39.67] you were laughing, I was almost breathless
[01:44.07] but in the spiral dawn
[01:48.88] we became one
[01:55.38] 
[02:30.03] Leave it to me to love you